headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
All Bunker properties are 40% off via Maze Bank Foreclosures, as are their Upgrades, Renovations and Modifications. Also get 40% off the Mobile Operations Center and all upgrades to it.

Beyond that, there is a selection of vehicles on sale including the below:

- Ocelot Jugular - 35% off
- Maibatsu Penumbra FF - 35% off
- Pegassi Tempesta - 35% off
- JoBuilt P-996 LAZER - 30% off

And more! Check out Rockstar Newswire for more details.
